Just 2 weeks remaining until the Great West Run and I still have some items to auction off for the foundation... A pair of signed Craig Noone boots, a pair of Stewart Fleetwood boots and a pair of Lawson D'ath boots that are currently at £50, if you'd like to make a bid on any of these items then just simply reply on this thread or tweet me - Tvickers1... Here's a link to my fundraising page if your feeling generous and just want to sponsor me... uk.virginmoneygiving.com/team/gwrstanno9

Thanks for view, up the City!!! #AS9
